<section class="manual-demo" aria-label="手动模式参数示意图">
  <div class="manual-demo__grid">
    <div class="manual-demo__card">
      <div class="manual-demo__badge">曝光不是越亮越对</div>
      <div class="manual-demo__scene manual-demo__scene--exposure">
        <div class="manual-demo__meter">
          <span class="manual-demo__tick">-</span>
          <span class="manual-demo__tick">0</span>
          <span class="manual-demo__tick">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="manual-demo__pointer"></div>
        <div class="manual-demo__note">先想保什么，再决定亮一点还是暗一点</div>
      </div>
      <p>曝光补偿和手动曝光最重要的，不是把画面拉到平均亮，而是主动决定你更想保住高光、暗部还是主体气氛。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="manual-demo__card">
      <div class="manual-demo__badge">参数是在换代价</div>
      <div class="manual-demo__scene manual-demo__scene--tradeoff">
        <div class="manual-demo__chip manual-demo__chip--shutter">快门</div>
        <div class="manual-demo__chip manual-demo__chip--iso">ISO</div>
        <div class="manual-demo__chip manual-demo__chip--wb">白平衡</div>
        <div class="manual-demo__line manual-demo__line--one"></div>
        <div class="manual-demo__line manual-demo__line--two"></div>
      </div>
      <p>快门、ISO、白平衡不是独立小游戏。你调一个，通常就要接受另一个代价，比如更亮但更脏，或更稳但更暗。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

